Study on slugs, carried out by scientists at Ruakura Agricultural Research
Centre, Hamilton, NZ. One of the goals of the study was to determine the
relationship between length and weight of slugs.

Citation:
Barker, G, and McGhie, R (1984) The Biology of Introduced Slugs (Pulmonata)
in New Zealand: Introduction and Notes on Limax Maximus, NZ Entomologist 8,
pp 106-111

